This song is dedicated to all the kids who never came back home on 16th of December... they didn't get martyred, nonetheless, they've the same rank as all of the martyrs. We're not afraid of the terrorism anymore,  but we're well aware of their cowardly acts. We're ready to sacrifice, and we'll keep on sacrificing. #NeverForget
#PakistanZindabad 🇵🇰
